{"tid":1471205,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場貼臨時禁制令限示威範圍　英國人：恐懼警方多於示威者","createTime":"2019-08-14T08:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T23:50:09.000Z","uid":53379,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"52ef94ac42c10b0b4547b7622f996bfc370217a9","tid":1471205,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:13:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>機場貼臨時禁制令限示威範圍　英國人：恐懼警方多於示威者</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n機場示威者昨日（13日）影響旅客出入境，再次釀成警民衝突。機管局於今日（14日）下午2時半左右，貼出臨時禁制令，表明只可在一號客運大樓入境大堂兩個指定區域進行示威活動。下午3時，機場仍有數十人於指定範圍內，繼續向旅客講解反送中議題，有來港工作的英國人表明不擔心受示威影響，但認為示威者要留意民意走向，又指警方近來的行為不專業和情緒化。<br />\n<br />\n來港工作4年的James Brown（化名）今日從英國回港，他指自己一直有留意反修例事件的走向，被問及近日機場的衝突會否影響他對香港的信心，他說：<br />\n我恐懼警方多於示威者，因為示威者大部份時間和平，但警察出現就動用武力<br />\n<br />\nBrown指，相比起英國警方，香港警方予人感覺情緒化、不專業、和準備不足；而英國警方驅散示威者時，多數只會使用盾牌和警棍，甚少使用催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n對於昨日有示威者堵塞機場離境大堂，Brown認為在爭取訴求的角度看，很難判別對錯，但個人認為未必是最好的做法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2425000/2426550/airport_002_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2425000%2F2426550%2Fairport_002_600.jpeg&h=e7c7469d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n機管局下午2時起於機場一號客運大樓實施進出管制安排。（陳靜儀攝）<br />\n<br />\n另一位來港工作的英國人Lucy Bellamy指，支持港人表達訴求的權力，但認為阻礙他人的做法欠妥當。她稱，雖然自己對香港熟悉所以不感到擔心，但由於新聞上永遠都是衝突的場景，相信會令首次來港的旅客對香港留下負面印象，亦感到擔心。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2426550?fbclid=IwAR0J-9ldLXXiHJu7p8eru6NNfgp7Twed6-GJFA_XBfDweSIOzVBB6D8wbXI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2426550%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0J-9ldLXXiHJu7p8eru6NNfgp7Twed6-GJFA_XBfDweSIOzVBB6D8wbXI&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3RVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=b0bd9b37\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2426550?fbclid=IwAR0J-9ldLXXiHJu7p8eru6NNfgp7Twed6-GJFA_XBfDweSIOzVBB6D8wbXI</a>"},{"pid":"dd40feef910a486d35c75429579ef88227cef41a","tid":1471205,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9020dca5b9172dc439e87a4b58c52c1f59fce03a","tid":1471205,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35680146e6fc3013c44b5d47006d9dcbff3d411d","tid":1471205,"uid":244230,"like":0,"disl